bilingual.source: He was really worried that his coach might kick him off the team.
bilingual.target: 他真的很担心教练会把他踢出队伍。

bilingual.source: He gave the football a hard kick.
He tried to kick the ball into the goal.
She gave him a swift kick in the arse.
bilingual.target: 她迅速踢了他一脚屁股。

bilingual.source: The horse will kick if you stand too close.
bilingual.target: 如果你站得太近，马会踢你。

bilingual.source: She loves to kick the punching bag during her workout.
bilingual.target: 她喜欢在锻炼时踢沙袋。

bilingual.source: The boss decided to kick out the lazy employee.
bilingual.target: 老板决定把那个懒惰的员工踢出公司。

bilingual.source: The player was penalized for trying to kick his opponent.
bilingual.target: 这名球员因试图踢对手而被罚。

bilingual.source: He learned how to kick properly in his karate class.
bilingual.target: 他在空手道课上学会了如何正确地踢。

bilingual.source: He tried to kick the door open.

list.abstract: kick（英[kɪk]，美[kɪk]），英语单词。可做名词或动词用。做名词时，指踢、刺激作用、凹底、踢球；做动词时，指踢腿、懊悔、举腿。英语短语有frog kick（蛙泳蹬腿），例句：Put both feet in, get in the water, and feel how it is to flap instead of kick.（将双脚放入水中，感受拍打而不是踢打的感觉。）

yingyinNormal.en: That's a kick. That's an actual kick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 踢了，孩子真的踢了一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, kick it away. Farther.
yingyinNormal.zh: 把它踢开, 踢远点。

yingyinNormal.en: But faster, OK? Now, claw, kick, claw, kick. I'm stalking the prey. Claw, kick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但速度要快一点，像这样，划、踢，划、踢 匍匐前进，划、踢。

yingyinNormal.en: Even simpler this time, kick the ball with your foot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这次更简单了，用你的脚踢球。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I don't want to hit you. Oh what then? Kick me? No. Bite me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我不想打你。什么？你要踢我？不咬我？

yingyinNormal.en: No, it's a gentle kick; you're doing it wrong. Here. Give me those.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，人家是轻踢，你没做到位。来，把东西都给我。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no. you're okay. If you run into crocodiles, just kick them with your boots.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，不，没事，如果你碰到鳄鱼，就用靴子踢它。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait. If she only has one leg, shouldn't she be on can't-kick-starter?
yingyinNormal.zh: 慢着，如果她只有一条腿，她应该去"踢不了人"那种网站才对吧。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't need my help when you can open the trunk with a simple kick of the foot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当轻轻一踢就可以打开后备箱时，你就根本不需要我帮忙了。

yingyinNormal.en: Julie, isn't that great? I mean, isn't that just kick-you-in-the-crotch, spit-on-your-neck fantastic?
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是太棒了！是不是像踢你的裤裆和朝你的脖子吐口水一样神奇？

yingyinNormal.en: What are you doing? I felt a kick. There's a baby in there. Oh, yeah, that's where I put it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在干嘛我感觉到踢了一下，里面有一个宝宝呢。对哦，原来我把宝宝放这里了。

yingyinNormal.en: All right, she's right. We gotta get serious. Let's put Styrofoam peanuts down his pants and kick him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她说的对，我们得认真一点儿。让我们把这个塞到他的裤裆里，然后踢他！

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, you missed, 'Takes money to make money,' and 'Don't make me come down there and kick your wall street butt.'
yingyinNormal.zh: 你错过了“用钱去赚钱”还有，“别逼我过去踢你的华尔街屁股”。

yingyinNormal.en: But he was faster than me, stronger than me and he would kick my butt, and we both knew that, so I just took it in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是他跑得比我快，长得比我壮，他会踢我的屁股，我们都知道，所以我只是默默承受。

yingyinNormal.en: I think what my colleague is saying is that you're not seeing the possibilities here. That is indeed one unbelievably kick ass computer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想我同事想说的是你没有看到这里面的潜力，这是一款另人难以置信的产品，可以把其它电脑一脚踢出门外。

yingyinNormal.en: He had worked tremendously hard pre-season, oh I was like, "man, this is a blow. I mean, this is a kick in the stomach right here."
yingyinNormal.zh: 他已经在赛季前付出了巨大的努力，所以我想，“天啊，这是一个大打击啊” 我的意思是，这就像一脚，刚好踢在你的肚子上

yingyinNormal.en: Can you hear a little heart beat? Yes, I can. It's going "Boom. Boom. Boom." Oh, it just moved. Yes, sometimes babies give a little kick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有没有听到小宝宝的心跳声？我听到了，就像这样，“砰！”“砰”！“砰！”哇，他刚才动了一下。是的，有时候小宝宝在里面会踢我肚子。

yingyinNormal.en: What a big house. Lots of room for a Queen to kick a ball about. Where is the Queen?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好大的房子！空间这么大，女王可以在这里踢球了。女王在哪里呢？

yingyinNormal.en: All right, so, shh! Tyra Banks is about to kick someone off America's Next Top Model.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，大家安静！泰拉·班克斯(超模之母)马上要从全美超模大赛里踢人了。

yingyinNormal.en: What a big house. Lots of room for a Queen to kick a ball about. Where is the Queen? Queen? Queen? Where are you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好大的房子！空间这么大，女王可以在这里踢球了。女王在哪里呢？女王，女王，你在哪里？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: For many men, the end of the workday is a time to <highlight>kick</highlight> back.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对很多男人来说，下班后就是放松的时候。

examination_example.sentence: Their home is also a place for <highlight>kicking</highlight> back.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们的家也是一个放松的地方。

sense_info_list.en: strike or propel forcibly with the foot

examination_example.sentence: We hail them as Americans in the making, or brand them as aliens to be <highlight>kicked</highlight> out.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们欢呼他们成为美国人，或者把他们贴上被驱逐的外星人的标签。

sense_info_list.en: to score points by kicking the ball
a strong feeling of excitement and pleasure

word_usage.usage: kick作动词时，既可作及物动词，又可作不及物动词。作及物动词时，其后可接名词或者代词，如：kick legs 踢腿。
kick作名词，表示“效力；刺激性”时，常用单数形式，如：This drink has quite a kick. 这种饮料很刺激。
